---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="CapCity Presents is led by Andy Moreno and books independent Olympia shows with DIY and all-ages values.">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container split">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
        <h1>About CapCity Presents</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="panel prose">
        <p>CapCity Presents started in Olympia in 2015, when Joey Cristina pulled together Andy Moreno and other local promoters to work under one name instead of treating every show like a turf war.</p>
        <p>Today, Andy is at the helm of CapCity's booking and promotion work, carrying the project forward across Olympia and Western Washington.</p>
        <p>The project came out of hardcore, punk, metal, and DIY spaces. That still matters. All-ages access is not a marketing angle here; it is an ethical standard.</p>
        <p>CapCity books and promotes local and touring artists with a focus on clear show information, strong local bills, and rooms that make sense for the artists and audience.</p>
        <div class="actions"><a class="button primary" href="/events/">See upcoming shows</a><a class="button" href="/contact/">Contact CapCity</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2>People</h2>
        <p>The people keeping CapCity Presents moving.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="people-grid">
        <article class="panel prose person-card">
          <p class="eyebrow">Lead booking / promotion</p>
          <h3>Andy "Remex" Moreno</h3>
          <p>Andy is the person currently steering CapCity Presents. He handles the main booking and promotion work, keeping the Olympia calendar moving and helping touring artists find their way into the right rooms.</p>
          <p>He began booking shows in November 2011 and became a steady Northwest contact for touring musicians, agents, and local artists looking to play Olympia.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="panel prose person-card">
          <p class="eyebrow">Founder / website admin</p>
          <h3>Joey Cristina</h3>
          <p>Joey started CapCity Presents in 2015 after years of booking DIY shows in Olympia and seeing too much needless competition in the local promoter scene.</p>
          <p>These days, Joey mostly keeps the website alive and jumps into booking when the itch hits. He has been booking and promoting in the area since as early as 2006, with hundreds of DIY shows behind him and a long-running commitment to all-ages access.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
